Case Study - Zomato Sales Decline Analysis 

Role - Business Analyst 
Prepared by - Sairaj More
Date - [ 26/06/2026 ]


Business Problem :
Problem Statement  : Zomato's Sales Declining Over the Last 6 Month's .
Objective          : Find the Root Cause and Recommended Data Driven Solution .


Key Clarifications : (Ask follow up Questions) 
                     1) Is the Decline in Sales , Revenue , Profit or Order ? 
                     2) Is this Affecting all Cites or Only Specific Region ?
                     3) Which Business Line is Impacted ?
                     4) Which Customer segment is Contributing to the Decline ?


Scopes and Assumptions : (Answers of the above Questions Given By the Data analyst and Interviewer)
                         1) Sales Decline      : 20%
                         2) Business Line      : Food Delivery 
                         3) Geography          : Mumbai 
                         4) Time Period        : Last 6 Months 
                         5) Customer Segments : Repeat Customer 


Make KPIs : 
           1) Sales Revenue                   - Primary KPI
           2) Average Order Value by Customer - Supporting KPI
           3) Customer Retention              - Supporting KPI
           4) Customer Churn                  - Supporting KPI



Breakdown Problem into 2 Different Factors : 
1) Internal Factor : 1) App Performance Issue - ( UI/UX design)
                     2) Checkout Failures
                     3) Delivery Delays 
                     4) Order Cancellation 
                     5) Customer Support Problem
                     6) Higher Platform Fees 
                     7) Reduced Discounts
                     
2) External Factor : 1) Other Market Competitors
                     2) Increasing Price / Price Sensitive Customer 
                     3) Inflation
                     4) Fuel Price Increasing for Home Delivery 
                     5) Change Food Preferences
                     6) Seasonal Demand Pattern 
                     




Hypothesis Foundation :

   Hypothesis                                  Validation 
1) Delivery Time Increased                     Delivery Time Report 
2) Platform Fee Increased                      Pricing Analysis 
3) Customer Compliant Increased                Compliant Dashboard 
4) Competitor Discount Improved                Market Research   
5) Add Performance Degraded                    Cash Report Analysis    



Prioritized Hypothesis :

1) Delivery Delay        - High 
2) Pricing Changes       - High
3) Customer Compliant    - High
4) Competitor Offer      - Medium
5) App Performance Issue - Medium



Data and Stakeholder Analysis :
  
  Data Required                               Stakeholder
1) Sales and Revenue Report                   Business Manager 
2) Order Trends                               Product Manager
3) Retention and Churn Data                   Marketing Team 
4) Delivery Time and Metrics                  Operations Team
5) Compliant and Refund Reports               Customer Support 
6) App Rating and Reviews                     Technology Team
7) Competitor and Pricing Data                Restaurant Partner Team



  
Finding and Root Cause Analysis :

1) Delivery     - 28 to 42 mins ( Delivery Time Increased )    >> 50% Slower Than Before 
2) Complaints   - +35 % ( Customer Complaint Increased )       >> Service Quality Concerns
3) Repat Orders - -18 % ( Repeat Customer Orders Declined )    >> Loyal Customer Ordering Less 



Root Cause Analysis 

Technique - ( Why 5 )    :
1) Why Sales Declined ?
2) Why Customers Ordered Less ?
3) why Delivery was consistently Delayed ?
4) why Insufficient delivery Partners during Peak hours ? 
5) Why Low incentive Structure reduced partner Availability ?


Root Cause Validated : 
Operational Inefficiencies combined with increased competition led to lower Customer satisfaction and reduced repeat orders




Recommended Solutions :

   0 - 3 Months                                         3 - 12 Months 
1) increase delivery partner incentives                 AI based Delivery Routing 
2) improve refund turnaround time                       Restaurant Performance Monitoring
3) targeted discounts for repeat customers              Pricing Strategy Redesign
4) Fix critical app issues                              Strengthen loyalty Program                 
5) Launch Retention campaigns                           Enhance App Scalability 




Prioritization Matrix :

   Recommendations :                         Priority :
1) Improve Delivery Operations               High
2) Enhance Customer Support                  High
3) Fix App Performance                       High 
4) Review Pricing Strategy                   Medium
5) Launch Loyalty Program                    Medium 
6) Technology Enhancement                    Low  



